---
title: Sweet & Sticky Asian Beef with Garlic Rice & Veggie Stir-Fry
description: There’s something seriously addictive about succulent beef strips coated in this sweet and sticky sauce, which has a touch of zing from the addition of ginger. Just add fragrant garlic rice and tender veggies for a meal that's sure to be a new favourite.
